<span class="code-comment">-- Get users with ordering</span>
<span class="code-comment">-- Request: GET /api/users?order_by=created_at&order_direction=DESC</span>
<span class="code-comment">-- Response: [{"id":100,"name":"Newest"},{"id":99,"name":"Older"},...]</span></code></pre>
